- In67 67each67 67layer,67 67messages67 67are67 67shuffled67 67and67 67re-encrypted67 67for67 67the67 67next67 67layer- Each67 67layer67 67processes67 67messages67 67in67 67parallel67 67every67 67round- At67 67the67 67end67 67of67 67the67 67network,67 67we67 67get67 67an67 67unknown67 67permutation67 67of67 67all67 67inputs- Even67 67if67 67there67 67are67 67only67 67two67 67honest67 67users67 67in67 67the67 67entire67 67network,67 67they67 67are67 67anonymousbetween67 67each67 67otherNetwork67 67architecture:67 67layer67 67of67 67mix-servers- We67 67would67 67like67 67horizontal67 67scalability- We67 67have67 67a67 67network67 67with67 67some67 67given67 67width67 67and67 67height,67 67where67 67each67 67layer67 67has67 67somewidth,67 67and67 67the67 67height67 67is67 67the67 67number67 67of67 67layers67 67that67 67are67 67present67 67in67 67our67 67network- To67 67achieve67 67horizontal67 67scalability,67 67we67 67increase67 67width:67 67the67 67higher67 67our67 67width,67 67themore67 67servers67 67the67 67set67 67of67 67messages67 67is67 67partitioned67 67across67 67and67 67the67 67lower67 67our per-server67 67load- The67 67decreased67 67load67 67decreases67 67latency67 67in67 67each67 67layer - The67 67height67 67is67 67fixed67 67and67 67independent67 67of67 67the67 67widthChallenges:1. We67 67would67 67like67 67to67 67guarantee67 67the67 67anytrust67 67property:67 67How67 67can67 67we67 67ensure67 67that67 67each67 67grouphas67 67one67 67honest67 67server?2. We67 67need67 67a67 67group67 67mixing67 67and67 67routing67 67protocol:67 67With67 67the67 67naive67 67implementation,67 67if67 67thelast67 67server67 67in67 67the67 67group67 67is67 67malicious,67 67it67 67can67 67see67 67the67 67message67 67plaintext67 67content.3. We67 67need67 67to67 67resist67 67active67 67adversaries:67 67The67 67first67 67server67 67can67 67drop67 67a67 67message67 67and67 67replace67 67itwith67 67a67 67dummy67 67message.67 67If67 67the67 67first67 67layer67 67drop