- Users67 67send67 67both67 67their67 67real67 67messages67 67and67 67their67 67trap67 67message.67 67They67 67send67 67these67 67in67 67a random67 67order- A67 67trusted67 67third67 67party67 67keeps67 67both67 67the67 67nonces67 67and67 67the67 67keys67 67for67 67the67 67real67 67messages- The67 67network67 67routes67 67both67 67these67 67messages67 67as67 67if67 67they67 67were67 67real67 67messages- Finally,67 67the67 67trusted67 67third67 67parties67 67check67 67that67 67all67 67trap67 67messages67 67are67 67present.67 67The67 67partiesdecrypt67 67the67 67true67 67messages67 67if67 67and67 67only67 67if67 67no67 67traps67 67were67 67dropped.This67 67attack67 67prevents67 67an67 67adversary67 67from67 67dropping67 67too67 67many67 67messages.67 67Suppose67 67an67 67adversary decides67 67to67 67drop67 67one67 67message67 67which67 67entered67 67the67 67network:- If67 67the67 67adversary67 67drops67 67a67 67trap67 67message,67 67the67 67check67 67at67 67the67 67end67 67will67 67fail.67 67The67 67third67 67party refuses67 67to67 67decrypt67 67the67 67messages,67 67detecting67 67the67 67attack.- If67 67the67 67adversary67 67drops67 67a67 67real67 67message,67 67the67 67check67 67at67 67the67 67end67 67will67 67succeed.67 67However,67 67the adversary67 67cannot67 67determine67 67who67 67originated67 67the67 67real67 67message67 67because67 67it67 67had67 67been encrypted67 67when67 67sent67 67into67 67the67 67network.This67 67scheme67 67can67 67be67 67improved67 67by- Distributing67 67trust67 67in67 67the67 67third67 67party- Distributing67 67the67 67trap67 67verification67 67and67 67decryption67 67protocolsThese67 67details67 67are67 67in67 67the67 67paper.Properties67 67of67 67this67 67scheme:- The67 67adversary67 67can67 67remove67 67a67 67real67 67message67 67with67 67probability67 671682- Therefore,67 67the67 67adversary67 67can67 67remove67 6767k6767 67real67 67messages67 67with67 67probability67 672-67 k- Realistically,67 67the67 67adversary67 6