RAPPOR:- The67 67largest67 67differentially-private67 67database67 67in67 67use- Involves67 67many67 67opt-in67 67statistics67 67which67 67are67 67obtained67 67by67 67Google67 67Chrome67 67as67 67they relate67 67to67 67multimedia67 67systems- Billions67 67of67 67reports67 67every67 67day- Unfortunately,67 67limited67 67in67 67scope:67 67only67 67applicable67 67to67 67large67 67datasets67 67and67 67bad67 67for67 67sparsedatasets- Statistical67 67in67 67nature- Adds67 67a67 67lot67 67of67 67noise- In67 67theory,67 67grows67 67with67 67sqrt(respondents)- In67 67practice,67 67much67 67worse67 67than67 67this67 67lower67 67bound- Even67 67with67 671TB67 67reports,67 67cannot67 67meaningfully67 67monitor67 67API67 67usageEncoding67 67fragments67 67and67 67crowds:Aside67 67from67 67differentially-private67 67encoding,67 67other67 67encodings67 67exist67 67(such67 67as67 67filter,67 67sample, fragment,67 67or67 67secret-share).67 67Fragments67 67can67 67hide67 67in67 67a67 67crowd67 67of67 67identical67 67fragments,67 67especially67 67for things67 67that67 67are67 67popular.67 67This67 67requires67 67some67 67notion67 67of67 67anonymity.Shuffling:Shuffling67 67is67 67a67 67useful67 67primitive67 67for67 67providing67 67anonymity67 67(for67 67example,67 67to67 67fragments)- Shuffling67 67process67 67strips67 67IP67 67addresses67 67and67 67metadata- Allows67 67processing67 67millions67 67of67 67items67 67every67 67day- Randomly67 67shuffling67 67reports67 67breaks67 67linkability67 67between67 67fragments--even67 67from67 67the67 67sameuser- Shuffling67 67removes67 67ordering67 67and67 67timing67 67informationWe67 67can67 67use67 67randomized67 67thresholds67 67to67 67give67 67crowd-blending67 67differential67 67privacy,67 67where67 67only data67 67above67 67a67 67certain67 67threshold67 67makes67 67it67 67through67 67the67 67shuffle.67 67This67 67may67 67also67 67be67 67used67 67for67 67the cryptographic67 67blinding67 67of67 67crowds.ESA67 67is67 67more