- Shuffle67 67scheme67 67is67 67the67 67last67 67stepEvaluation:- Set67 67the67 67security67 67parameter67 67to67 67give67 67a67 67nearly67 67uniformly67 67random67 67shuffle67 67(at67 672-67 8067)- Latency:67 67at67 67most67 674.167 67hours- Reasonable67 67for67 67Google67 67API67 67datasetsBenchmark:67 67How67 67much67 67data67 67can67 67you67 67reconstruct67 67from67 67an67 67anonymized67 67corpus67 67of67 67words collected67 67from67 67social67 67media?- Prochlo67 67compares67 67well67 67with67 67prior67 67work,67 67especially67 67k-anonymity67 67(NoCowd),67 67which67 67is reconstructed67 67poorly67 67at67 67first67 67but67 67whose67 67recovery67 67scales67 67quickly67 67at67 67larger67 67sizesMore67 67experiments67 67are67 67in67 67the67 67paper.Models67 67are67 67competitive67 67with67 67the67 67Netflix67 67challenge.67 67Prochlo67 67supports67 67a67 67recommendation67 67enginewith67 67strong67 67differential67 67privacy.Open-source67 67efforts:- Prochlo67 67(includes67 67implementation67 67of67 67shuffler)- Cobalt67 67(as67 67part67 67of67 67the67 67Fuschia67 67system)- Also67 67in67 67RAPPORQ&A:Q:67 67Bryan67 67Ford,67 67Ecole67 67Polytechnique67 67Federale67 67de67 67Lausanne:67 67Prochlo67 67uses67 67SGX67 67for67 67security67 67of67 67its execution.67 67Isn’t67 67this67 67shifting67 67trust67 67assumptions67 67from67 67Google67 67to67 67Intel?A:67 67We67 67try67 67to67 67use67 67an67 67architecture67 67that67 67is67 67realistic67 67in67 67the67 67real67 67world67 67today.67 67We67 67want67 67to67 67limit67 67data sent67 67by67 67clients67 67(in67 67encoding),67 67protect67 67it67 67as67 67soon67 67as67 67it67 67arrives,67 67and67 67protect67 67it67 67during67 67analysis. Google67 67does67 67all67 67steps.67 67SGX67 67is67 67sufficient67 67for67 67protecting67 67data67 67from67 67datacenter67 67operators.67 67More guarantees,67 67though,67 67are67 67always67 67better.Q:67 67Brad67 67Karp,67 67Google67 67Inc.:67 67Differential67 67privacy67